      "width": 500,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "⚙️ GPU VRAM Requirements:\n\n   Model               VRAM     Quality\n   ─────────────────────────────────────\n   qwen3-coder         ~16GB    ★★★★★\n   glm-4.7-flash       ~21GB    ★★★★☆\n   devstral-small(24B) ~14GB    ★★★★☆\n   qwen2.5-coder:7b    ~5GB     ★★★☆☆  (budget)",
